to it appear to curve away.

00:09:46.200 --> 00:09:49.260
What's remarkable is that
Bolyai didn't have a model

00:09:49.260 --> 00:09:51.180
of hyperbolic geometry yet,

00:09:51.180 --> 00:09:54.330
