triangles with the assumption

00:09:54.330 --> 00:09:56.940
that Euclid's fifth postulate didn't hold.

00:09:56.940 --> 00:09:58.710
And while Bolyai found

00:09:58.710 --> 00:10:00.570
that the behavior in hyperbolic geometry

00:10:00.570 --> 00:10:02.730
is very different than Euclid's,

00:10:02.730 --> 00:10:06.114
mathematically, it seemed
just as consistent.

00:10:06.114 --> 00:10:07.770
(soft music)

00:10:07.770 --> 00:10:11.977
In 1823, the 20-year-old
János wrote to his dad,

00:10:11.977 --> 00:10:16.290
"I have discovered such wonderful
things that I was amazed.

00:10:16.290 --> 00:10:20.907
Out of nothing, I have created
a strange new universe."

00:10:23.991 --> 00:10:24.824
(contemplative music)

00:10:24.824 --> 00:10:25.680
But Bolyai had been doing more

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:28.320
