00:10:45.810 --> 00:10:47.250
from his superiors.

00:10:47.250 --> 00:10:50.190
That made him hard to get along with.

00:10:50.190 --> 00:10:53.070
This reached a peak when,
during one of his deployments,

00:10:53.070 --> 00:10:55.500
13 cavalry officers from his garrison

00:10:55.500 --> 00:10:57.453
challenged him to a duel.

00:10:58.470 --> 00:11:00.090
Bolyai accepted their challenge,

00:11:00.090 --> 00:11:02.430
on the condition that
after every two duels,

00:11:02.430 --> 00:11:05.820
