while on his violin.

00:11:05.820 --> 00:11:08.220
Bolyai fought each of them in succession,

00:11:08.220 --> 00:11:10.410
winning all 13 duels,

00:11:10.410 --> 00:11:13.863
and leaving behind all his
adversaries on the square.

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:17.160
While Bolyai loved dueling,

00:11:17.160 --> 00:11:19.620
his first love was still mathematics.

00:11:19.620 --> 00:11:21.030
In 1832,

00:11:21.030 --> 00:11:24.360
9 years after he discovered
his strange new universe,

00:11:24.360 --> 00:11:27.360
